<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" itunes:timing="Word"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="drop dead"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Olivia Rodrigo"/><amll:meta key="album" value="you seem pretty sad for a girl so in love"/><amll:meta key="isrc" value="USUG12601721"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="3370511577"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="6gkbtMtioHgtyGjrMel6ei"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="0019pnwy4MlXc0"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="142093212"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="iiiooi"/></metadata></head><body dur="3:42.017"><div begin="15.178" end="3:42.017"><p begin="15.178" end="20.042" itunes:key="L1" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="15.178" end="15.625">I</span> <span begin="15.625" end="16.072">know</span> <span begin="16.072" end="16.382">that</span> <span begin="16.382" end="16.658">the</span> <span begin="16.658" end="17.155">bar</span> <span begin="17.155" end="17.931">closes</span> <span begin="17.931" end="18.402">at</span> <span begin="18.402" end="20.042">11</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我知道酒吧在十一点关门</span></p><p begin="22.232" end="27.621" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="22.232" end="22.527">But</span> <span begin="22.527" end="22.975">I</span> <span begin="22.975" end="23.399">hope</span> <span begin="23.399" end="23.789">you</span> <span begin="23.789" end="24.485">never</span> <span begin="24.485" end="25.511">finish</span> <span begin="25.511" end="25.959">that</span> <span begin="25.959" end="27.621">beer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">但我希望你永远别喝完那杯啤酒</span></p><p begin="29.919" end="34.799" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="29.919" end="30.376">You</span> <span begin="30.376" end="30.766">know</span> <span begin="30.766" end="31.179">all</span> <span begin="31.179" end="31.466">the</span> <span begin="31.466" end="32.062">words</span> <span begin="32.062" end="32.424">to</span> <span begin="32.424" end="32.781">&quot;Just</span> <span begin="32.781" end="33.281">Like</span> <span begin="33.281" end="33.611">Hea</span><span begin="33.611" end="34.799">ven&quot;</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你对《Just Like Heaven》的歌词了如指掌</span></p><p begin="35.229" end="37.943" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="35.229" end="35.477">And</span> <span begin="35.477" end="35.871">I</span> <span begin="35.871" end="36.136">know</span> <span begin="36.136" end="36.519">why</span> <span begin="36.519" end="37.022">he</span> <span begin="37.022" end="37.462">wrote</span> <span begin="37.462" end="37.943">them</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我也终于明白了作者写下它们的心境</span></p><p begin="37.943" end="43.270" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="37.943" end="38.445">Now</span> <span begin="38.445" end="38.915">that</span> <span begin="38.915" end="39.285">you&apos;re</span> <span begin="39.285" end="40.325">standing</span> <span begin="40.325" end="40.773">right</span> <span begin="40.773" end="43.270">here</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">而现在，你就站在我面前</span></p><p begin="43.758" end="47.918" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="43.758" end="44.753">Oh,</span> <span begin="44.753" end="45.154">one</span> <span begin="45.154" end="45.515">night</span> <span begin="45.515" end="46.030">I</span> <span begin="46.030" end="46.446">was</span> <span begin="46.446" end="46.936">bored</span> <span begin="46.936" end="47.404">in</span> <span begin="47.404" end="47.918">bed</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">哦，有天晚上我无聊地躺在床上</span></p><p begin="47.918" end="51.631" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="47.918" end="48.178">And</span> <span begin="48.178" end="48.794">stalked</span> <span begin="48.794" end="49.233">you</span> <span begin="49.233" end="49.703">on</span> <span begin="49.703" end="50.208">the</span> <span begin="50.208" end="50.596">in</span><span begin="50.596" end="51.151">ter</span><span begin="51.151" end="51.631">net</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在互联网上偷偷翻看你的动态</span></p><p begin="51.631" end="55.228" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="51.631" end="52.030">It&apos;s</span> <span begin="52.030" end="52.440">f</span><span begin="52.440" end="52.938">emi</span><span begin="52.938" end="53.399">nine</span> <span begin="53.399" end="53.813">in</span><span begin="53.813" end="54.423">tui</span><span begin="54.423" end="55.228">tion</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">那是女人的直觉在作祟</span></p><p begin="55.228" end="59.072" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="55.228" end="55.552">&apos;Cause</span> <span begin="55.552" end="55.741">I</span> <span begin="55.741" end="56.182">always</span> <span begin="56.182" end="56.425">had</span> <span begin="56.425" end="56.664">a</span> <span begin="56.664" end="57.102">vision</span> <span begin="57.102" end="57.347">of</span> <span begin="57.347" end="57.502">us</span> <span begin="57.502" end="57.939">standing</span> <span begin="57.939" end="58.370">like</span> <span begin="58.370" end="59.072">this</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">因为我脑海中总浮现出我们此刻站在一起的画面</span></p><p begin="59.072" end="1:02.592" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="59.072" end="59.417">All</span> <span begin="59.417" end="59.947">pressed</span> <span begin="59.947" end="1:00.268">up</span> <span begin="1:00.268" end="1:00.737">in</span> <span begin="1:00.737" end="1:01.152">the</span> <span begin="1:01.152" end="1:01.604">bath</span><span begin="1:01.604" end="1:02.099">room</span> <span begin="1:02.099" end="1:02.592">line</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在洗手间的排队队伍中紧紧相依</span></p><p begin="1:02.592" end="1:06.427" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:02.592" end="1:03.227">You</span> <span begin="1:03.227" end="1:03.529">looking</span> <span begin="1:03.529" end="1:03.761">like</span> <span begin="1:03.761" end="1:04.050">an</span> <span begin="1:04.050" end="1:04.509">angel</span> <span begin="1:04.509" end="1:04.740">on</span> <span begin="1:04.740" end="1:04.942">the</span> <span begin="1:04.942" end="1:05.152">walls</span> <span begin="1:05.152" end="1:05.370">of</span> <span begin="1:05.370" end="1:06.427">Versailles</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你看起来就像凡尔赛宫墙上的天使</span></p><p begin="1:06.427" end="1:10.045" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:06.427" end="1:06.799">The</span> <span begin="1:06.799" end="1:07.147">most</span> <span begin="1:07.147" end="1:08.102">alive</span> <span begin="1:08.102" end="1:08.617">I&apos;ve</span> <span begin="1:08.617" end="1:09.457">ever</span> <span begin="1:09.457" end="1:10.045">been</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这是我此生感到最鲜活的时刻</span></p><p begin="1:10.045" end="1:14.118" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:10.045" end="1:10.523">But</span> <span begin="1:10.523" end="1:10.913">kiss</span> <span begin="1:10.913" end="1:11.461">me,</span> <span begin="1:11.461" end="1:11.926">and</span> <span begin="1:11.926" end="1:12.328">I</span> <span begin="1:12.328" end="1:12.753">might</span> <span begin="1:12.753" end="1:13.226">drop</span> <span begin="1:13.226" end="1:14.118">dead</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">但如果你吻我，我也许会幸福得晕过去</span></p><p begin="1:21.781" end="1:23.021" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:21.781" end="1:21.853">And</span> <span begin="1:21.853" end="1:21.954">I</span> <span begin="1:21.954" end="1:22.111">feel</span> <span begin="1:22.111" end="1:22.246">like</span> <span begin="1:22.246" end="1:22.403">I</span> <span begin="1:22.403" end="1:22.521">might</span> <span begin="1:22.521" end="1:22.761">throw</span> <span begin="1:22.761" end="1:23.021">up</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">那种感觉就像胃里在翻江倒海</span></p><p begin="1:23.536" end="1:25.160" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:23.536" end="1:23.735">Left</span> <span begin="1:23.735" end="1:23.971">hook,</span> <span begin="1:23.971" end="1:24.213">right</span> <span begin="1:24.213" end="1:24.423">punch</span> <span begin="1:24.423" end="1:24.618">to</span> <span begin="1:24.618" end="1:24.738">the</span> <span begin="1:24.738" end="1:25.160">gut</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">像内心遭到重创</span></p><p begin="1:25.356" end="1:26.826" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:25.356" end="1:25.528">You&apos;re</span> <span begin="1:25.528" end="1:25.786">so,</span> <span begin="1:25.786" end="1:26.008">so</span> <span begin="1:26.008" end="1:26.378">pretty,</span> <span begin="1:26.378" end="1:26.826">boy</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你是个俊美无比的男孩</span></p><p begin="1:26.826" end="1:28.650" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:26.826" end="1:26.963">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="1:26.963" end="1:27.173">pa</span><span begin="1:27.173" end="1:27.388">ra</span><span begin="1:27.388" end="1:27.698">noid</span> <span begin="1:27.698" end="1:27.855">I</span> <span begin="1:27.855" end="1:28.045">made</span> <span begin="1:28.045" end="1:28.293">you</span> <span begin="1:28.293" end="1:28.650">up</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我甚至开始怀疑你是否我幻想出来的</span></p><p begin="1:29.023" end="1:30.486" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:29.023" end="1:29.153">Yeah,</span> <span begin="1:29.153" end="1:29.249">I&apos;d</span> <span begin="1:29.249" end="1:29.407">love</span> <span begin="1:29.407" end="1:29.539">it</span> <span begin="1:29.539" end="1:29.648">if</span> <span begin="1:29.648" end="1:29.771">you</span> <span begin="1:29.771" end="1:29.906">walked</span> <span begin="1:29.906" end="1:30.164">me</span> <span begin="1:30.164" end="1:30.486">home</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">是啊，假如你能送我回家，我会很开心的</span></p><p begin="1:30.924" end="1:32.519" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:30.924" end="1:30.986">If</span> <span begin="1:30.986" end="1:31.074">you</span> <span begin="1:31.074" end="1:31.349">promise,</span> <span begin="1:31.349" end="1:31.474">we</span> <span begin="1:31.474" end="1:31.644">can</span> <span begin="1:31.644" end="1:31.829">go</span> <span begin="1:31.829" end="1:31.997">real</span> <span begin="1:31.997" end="1:32.519">slow</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如果你能保证，我们可以走慢点</span></p><p begin="1:32.727" end="1:34.119" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:32.727" end="1:32.852">&apos;Cause</span> <span begin="1:32.852" end="1:33.142">I</span> <span begin="1:33.142" end="1:33.341">got</span> <span begin="1:33.341" end="1:33.749">chewing</span> <span begin="1:33.749" end="1:34.119">gum</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">因为我带了口香糖</span></p><p begin="1:34.135" end="1:35.903" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:34.135" end="1:34.258">And</span> <span begin="1:34.258" end="1:34.395">a</span> <span begin="1:34.395" end="1:34.561">bunch</span> <span begin="1:34.561" end="1:34.713">of</span> <span begin="1:34.713" end="1:34.913">stuff</span> <span begin="1:34.913" end="1:35.061">I&apos;d</span> <span begin="1:35.061" end="1:35.301">like</span> <span begin="1:35.301" end="1:35.543">to</span> <span begin="1:35.543" end="1:35.903">know</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">还有一堆想了解你的事情</span></p><p begin="1:35.903" end="1:37.776" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:35.903" end="1:36.143">Like,</span> <span begin="1:36.381" end="1:36.506">have</span> <span begin="1:36.506" end="1:36.628">you</span> <span begin="1:36.628" end="1:36.883">ever</span> <span begin="1:36.883" end="1:37.066">been</span> <span begin="1:37.066" end="1:37.270">to</span> <span begin="1:37.270" end="1:37.776">Japan?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">比如，你有没有去过日本？</span></p><p begin="1:37.776" end="1:39.641" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:37.776" end="1:37.958">Or</span> <span begin="1:37.958" end="1:38.173">taken</span> <span begin="1:38.173" end="1:38.378">that</span> <span begin="1:38.378" end="1:39.101">Eurostar</span> <span begin="1:39.101" end="1:39.323">to</span> <span begin="1:39.323" end="1:39.641">France?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">或者坐过那趟去法国的欧洲之星列车？</span></p><p begin="1:40.085" end="1:41.421" itunes:key="L24" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:40.085" end="1:40.218">I&apos;ve</span> <span begin="1:40.218" end="1:40.353">been</span> <span begin="1:40.353" end="1:40.645">dropping</span> <span begin="1:40.645" end="1:40.883">hints</span> <span begin="1:40.883" end="1:41.116">all</span> <span begin="1:41.116" end="1:41.421">night</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">或者坐过那趟去法国的欧洲之星列车？</span></p><p begin="1:41.481" end="1:43.561" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:41.481" end="1:41.489">That</span> <span begin="1:41.489" end="1:41.571">I&apos;d</span> <span begin="1:41.571" end="1:41.692">love</span> <span begin="1:41.692" end="1:41.849">it</span> <span begin="1:41.849" end="1:41.986">if</span> <span begin="1:41.986" end="1:42.114">you</span> <span begin="1:42.114" end="1:42.252">held</span> <span begin="1:42.252" end="1:42.472">my</span> <span begin="1:42.472" end="1:42.787">hand,</span> <span begin="1:42.787" end="1:42.996">god</span><span begin="1:42.996" end="1:43.561">damn</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">或者坐过那趟去法国的欧洲之星列车？</span></p><p begin="1:43.768" end="1:45.300" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:43.768" end="1:43.821">And</span> <span begin="1:43.821" end="1:43.926">then</span> <span begin="1:43.926" end="1:44.168">maybe</span> <span begin="1:44.168" end="1:44.303">we</span> <span begin="1:44.303" end="1:44.426">could</span> <span begin="1:44.426" end="1:44.688">make-</span><span begin="1:44.688" end="1:45.300">makeout</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">然后也许我们可以亲吻、亲热</span></p><p begin="1:45.523" end="1:46.991" itunes:key="L27" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:45.523" end="1:45.753">Clothes</span> <span begin="1:45.753" end="1:46.013">off</span> <span begin="1:46.013" end="1:46.140">and</span> <span begin="1:46.140" end="1:46.438">fall</span> <span begin="1:46.438" end="1:46.578">to</span> <span begin="1:46.578" end="1:46.694">the</span> <span begin="1:46.694" end="1:46.991">ground</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">脱掉外衣，一起倒在地上</span></p><p begin="1:47.168" end="1:48.783" itunes:key="L28" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:47.168" end="1:47.268">Let&apos;s</span> <span begin="1:47.268" end="1:47.523">go</span> <span begin="1:47.523" end="1:48.071">steady,</span> <span begin="1:48.071" end="1:48.231">let&apos;s</span> <span begin="1:48.231" end="1:48.493">go</span> <span begin="1:48.493" end="1:48.783">out</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">让我们正式交往吧，约会吧</span></p><p begin="1:48.840" end="1:50.882" itunes:key="L29" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:48.840" end="1:48.977">And</span> <span begin="1:48.977" end="1:49.207">tell</span> <span begin="1:49.207" end="1:49.390">the</span> <span begin="1:49.390" end="1:49.580">whole</span> <span begin="1:49.580" end="1:49.866">damn</span> <span begin="1:49.866" end="1:50.392">world</span> <span begin="1:50.392" end="1:50.882">how</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">告诉全世界这一切是怎样开始的</span></p><p begin="1:50.882" end="1:54.124" itunes:key="L30" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:50.882" end="1:51.289">One</span> <span begin="1:51.289" end="1:51.716">night</span> <span begin="1:51.716" end="1:52.112">I</span> <span begin="1:52.112" end="1:52.629">was</span> <span begin="1:52.629" end="1:53.102">bored</span> <span begin="1:53.102" end="1:53.576">in</span> <span begin="1:53.576" end="1:54.124">bed</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">哦,