.341" end="2:47.569">just</span> <span begin="2:47.569" end="2:47.776">have</span> <span begin="2:47.776" end="2:48.004">to</span> <span begin="2:48.004" end="2:48.581">stay</span> <span begin="2:48.581" end="2:49.021">for</span><span begin="2:49.021" end="2:49.479">e</span><span begin="2:49.479" end="2:49.974">ver</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我想我可能得永远留下来了</span></p><p begin="3:03.921" end="3:07.925" itunes:key="L46" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:03.921" end="3:04.812">Oh,</span> <span begin="3:04.812" end="3:05.122">one</span> <span begin="3:05.122" end="3:05.554">night</span> <span begin="3:05.554" end="3:06.046">I</span> <span begin="3:06.046" end="3:06.452">was</span> <span begin="3:06.452" end="3:06.922">bored</span> <span begin="3:06.922" end="3:07.389">in</span> <span begin="3:07.389" end="3:07.925">bed</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">哦,有天晚上我无聊地躺在床上</span></p><p begin="3:07.925" end="3:11.688" itunes:key="L47" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:07.925" end="3:08.178">And</span> <span begin="3:08.368" end="3:08.815">stalked</span> <span begin="3:08.815" end="3:09.306">you</span> <span begin="3:09.306" end="3:09.701">on</span> <span begin="3:09.701" end="3:10.261">the</span> <span begin="3:10.261" end="3:10.626">in</span><span begin="3:10.626" end="3:11.021">ter</span><span begin="3:11.021" end="3:11.688">net</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在互联网上偷偷翻看你的动态</span></p><p begin="3:11.688" end="3:15.301" itunes:key="L48" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:11.688" end="3:12.065">It&apos;s</span> <span begin="3:12.065" end="3:12.493">f</span><span begin="3:12.493" end="3:13.015">emi</span><span begin="3:13.015" end="3:13.465">nine</span> <span begin="3:13.465" end="3:13.851">in</span><span begin="3:13.851" end="3:14.346">tui</span><span begin="3:14.346" end="3:15.301">tion</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">那是女人的直觉在作祟</span></p><p begin="3:15.301" end="3:19.050" itunes:key="L49" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:15.301" end="3:15.551">&apos;Cause</span> <span begin="3:15.551" end="3:15.726">I</span> <span begin="3:15.726" end="3:16.198">always</span> <span begin="3:16.198" end="3:16.481">had</span> <span begin="3:16.481" end="3:16.691">a</span> <span begin="3:16.691" end="3:17.145">vision</span> <span begin="3:17.145" end="3:17.398">of</span> <span begin="3:17.398" end="3:17.563">us</span> <span begin="3:17.563" end="3:18.060">standing</span> <span begin="3:18.060" end="3:18.461">like</span> <span begin="3:18.461" end="3:19.050">this</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">因为我脑海中总浮现出我们此刻站在一起的画面</span></p><p begin="3:19.050" end="3:22.661" itunes:key="L50" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:19.050" end="3:19.496">All</span> <span begin="3:19.496" end="3:19.793">pressed</span> <span begin="3:19.793" end="3:20.305">up</span> <span begin="3:20.305" end="3:20.749">in</span> <span begin="3:20.749" end="3:21.235">the</span> <span begin="3:21.235" end="3:21.690">bath</span><span begin="3:21.690" end="3:22.176">room</span> <span begin="3:22.176" end="3:22.661">line</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在洗手间的排队队伍中紧紧相依</span></p><p begin="3:22.661" end="3:26.419" itunes:key="L51" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:22.661" end="3:23.068">You</span> <span begin="3:23.068" end="3:23.570">looking</span> <span begin="3:23.570" end="3:23.791">like</span> <span begin="3:23.791" end="3:24.003">an</span> <span begin="3:24.003" end="3:24.498">angel</span> <span begin="3:24.498" end="3:24.761">on</span> <span begin="3:24.761" end="3:24.968">the</span> <span begin="3:24.968" end="3:25.251">walls</span> <span begin="3:25.251" end="3:25.446">of</span> <span begin="3:25.446" end="3:26.419">Versailles</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你看起来就像凡尔赛宫墙上的天使</span></p><p begin="3:26.419" end="3:30.083" itunes:key="L52" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:26.419" end="3:26.852">The</span> <span begin="3:26.852" end="3:27.292">most</span> <span begin="3:27.292" end="3:28.253">alive</span> <span begin="3:28.253" end="3:28.669">I&apos;ve</span> <span begin="3:28.669" end="3:29.498">ever</span> <span begin="3:29.498" end="3:30.083">been</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这是我此生感到最鲜活的时刻</span></p><p begin="3:30.083" end="3:34.200" itunes:key="L53" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:30.083" end="3:30.520">But</span> <span begin="3:30.520" end="3:30.962">kiss</span> <span begin="3:30.962" end="3:31.375">me</span> <span begin="3:31.375" end="3:31.830">and</span> <span begin="3:31.830" end="3:32.312">I</span> <span begin="3:32.312" end="3:34.200">might—</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">但如果你吻我，我可能会——</span></p><p begin="3:34.200" end="3:37.895" itunes:key="L54" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:34.200" end="3:34.672">Kiss</span> <span begin="3:34.672" end="3:35.139">me,</span> <span begin="3:35.139" end="3:35.565">and</span> <span begin="3:35.565" end="3:36.018">I</span> <span begin="3:36.018" end="3:37.895">might—</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你吻我，我可能会——</span></p><p begin="3:37.895" end="3:42.017" itunes:key="L55" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:37.895" end="3:38.367">Kiss</span> <span begin="3:38.367" end="3:38.859">me,</span> <span begin="3:38.859" end="3:39.285">and</span> <span begin="3:39.285" end="3:39.772">I</span> <span begin="3:39.772" end="3:40.185">might</span> <span begin="3:40.185" end="3:40.603">drop</span> <span begin="3:40.603" end="3:42.017">dead</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">但如果你吻我，我也许会幸福得晕过去</span></p></div></body></tt>